Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:15.15,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he was the top of his class at his previous school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:17.89,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I hope all of you study just as hard as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:20.81,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nishimi. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:21.81,Default-up,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Yokosuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.81,0:02:23.08,Default-up,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that pretty far?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:24.83,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm used to this routine. But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:26.43,Default-up,Student,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like a real bookworm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:27.64,Default-up,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Spoiled rich kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:28.79,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their unreserved stares...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:33.34,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their Kyushu dialect that I can't even follow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:39.76,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the most memorable welcome I've received yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:49.13,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-kun. Nishimi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:51.45,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided which club you're gonna join?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:53.28,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested in radios?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:55.64,Default,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Look at those losers, Maruo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.70,Default,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Two four-eyed bookworm runts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:59.44,Default,Student,0000,0000,0000,,They're made for each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:04.64,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry. Because of me, they picked on you too.
