Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.67,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:15.01,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:16.51,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in radios either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:23.76,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-kun, just one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:28.31,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a good idea to mess with the guy who sits behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:31.81,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,He's a notorious thug that even the teacher can't handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:35.40,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Kawabuchi, and if he zeros in on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:36.65,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:42.23,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, no. Just thinking about it makes me feel nauseous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:45.85,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)}Nishimi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:47.22,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.91,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the class representative, Mukae Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:55.87,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I was instructed to show you around the school during the lunch break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:57.72,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.89,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... don't feel sick anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:14.60,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,So the gymnasium is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:18.32,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And the infirmary is in this building...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:21.56,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay, Nishimi-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.17,Default,Ritsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:26.09,Default,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops! It slipped outta my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.17,Default,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:28.00,Default-up,Student,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:29.67,Default-up,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:31.16,Default-up,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Never seen him before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:37.12,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Mukae-san, where's the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:43.65,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've moved from school to school ever since first grade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:48.76,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If something unexpected happened, I would lose my balance,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:52.14,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and even minor stress would trigger nausea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:58.02,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But one time, I found a place at school where I could regain my bearings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:02.40,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. If I can just get to the roof...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:07.36,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:24.34,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:27.25,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,...came for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:34.24,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.75,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you holdin' my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.10,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that grabbed {\i1}my{\i0} hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:43.77,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I get it... You're the key burglar, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.56,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I ain't gonna hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:51.14,Default,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Sentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:53.62,Default,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you're lookin' for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:56.62,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Then you goons are the thieves, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:06:00.40,Default,Student,0000,0000,0000,,The roof belongs to us third-year smokers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:02.84,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:05.77,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I want the key to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:09.34,Default,Student,0000,0000,0000,,A wimp like you better get the hell outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:18.10,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You want the key that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.90,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.69,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hold this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:04.45,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:06.61,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:13.65,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,How reckless can you be, going up against three third-years?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.30,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you wanted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:21.17,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.84,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.29,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,For 100,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.62,0:07:31.08,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you thought I'd give it to you for nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:33.74,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I put my ass on the line gettin' it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.66,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,100,000 is cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:37.02,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:39.06,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm goin' home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:42.32,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I didn't even go to class once today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:50.80,Default-up,Student,0000,0000,0000,,A city boy like that's got no common ground with us country boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:56.01,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you, Sentaro! You got into another fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:58.16,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's just some scratches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.59,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:06.71,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Rikko, who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:10.96,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna answer a guy who does nothin' but fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.23,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Maruo! Talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:18.70,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's a new transfer student, Nishimi Kaoru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:22.37,Default,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,He's supposed to be rich and a real brainiac...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:24.45,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:27.32,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Maruo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.67,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there, rich boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:35.35,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, your name is "Bon."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:37.00,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let's you and me be chums, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:39.15,Default-up,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro's got a new target.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:40.56,Default-up,Student,0000,0000,0000,,It's curtains for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:42.21,Default-up,Student,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:44.82,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, no... I feel sick again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:48.06,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I've got a favor to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:48.89,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:53.85,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,100,000 is impossible, but could you lend me the key this once?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:56.19,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:08:58.27,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But right now it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:01.85,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's comin' down cats 'n dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:04.20,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,There's no problem if I take an umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:10.10,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a blast! I'm comin' too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:18.12,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.84,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't much fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.20,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.99,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not up here to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.81,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Then why bother comin' up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:28.58,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If you're bored, you can always go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:29.59,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.98,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Class ain't my scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:03.45,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.16,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving me the creeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:17.29,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:22.66,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon, you should take a shower too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:24.99,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.65,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,᠎What are you scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:31.84,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nothin' good has ever come from fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:34.16,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let yourself get a little wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:43.41,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.31,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're both...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:47.47,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:48.83,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Giving me trouble to no end...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:51.73,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,We're going straight to the infirmary, so you can borrow a towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:56.39,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. I'll get your gym clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:10:57.89,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll meet you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:17.28,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Is that... jazz?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:22.29,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What, you can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:23.78,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:25.33,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I play piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:27.18,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Classical music, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:31.04,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Classical, huh? What a drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:32.83,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.35,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's the nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:37.41,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:40.84,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.77,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice with your glasses on,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.77,0:11:45.36,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,but you have a really pretty face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.08,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-What...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:50.23,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it rude to call a man "pretty"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.52,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I meant "handsome."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.43,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:11:59.28,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.31,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a human hair dryer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.17,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:05.24,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,There he goes again, bein' scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.17,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What a fraidy cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:08.66,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:09.54,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:12.03,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,How could I be afraid anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.02,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:20.13,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that rain felt way better than I imagined.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:26.86,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's weird.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:31.24,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even with everyone staring at me, I can breathe normally.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:34.98,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of magic is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:45.16,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:48.41,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to play the piano, even though you're a sailor...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:54.12,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, I'm going to be away again for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:55.88,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Be a good boy while I'm gone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:59.63,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I play the piano, I can forget all of the bad stuff{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:03.14,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the loneliness from Dad being away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:05.30,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:10.49,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Your uncle in Kyushu has a huge grand piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:15.52,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dad... I don't want a grand piano.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:17.65,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What I want is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:30.33,Default,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kaoru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:32.72,Default,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,You're up pretty early today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.96,Default,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna play the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:36.22,Default,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:40.10,Default,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear a tune that'd wake me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:42.90,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But playing this early—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.61,Default,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanna hear it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:49.13,Default,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take responsibility, so please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:51.69,Default,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Please, please, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:51.69,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:11.22,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dad... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:19.01,Default,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me? What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.00,Default,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,Playing the piano at this hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.56,Default,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:25.34,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:26.30,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Mariko-chan—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.34,Default,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:30.13,Default,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I told you to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:33.06,Default,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,Putting the blame on someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:36.61,Default,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's difficult for a father to raise a child {\i1}alone{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:44.01,Default,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's your mother who's responsible, abandoning the both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:46.50,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:49.23,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Mukae-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:51.50,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro didn't come today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:54.91,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lonely without Sentaro here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:56.41,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.24,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to comprehend that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:01.96,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be quite pleased if he sees fit to extend his absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:04.44,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:07.39,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It looked to me like you two were hitting it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:11.29,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else is afraid of Sentaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:14.80,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,but you act normally in front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:19.74,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you and Sentaro could become buddies, Nishimi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.19,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mukae-san... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.12,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Give me a break with that smile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:28.31,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Really, as his childhood friend, I can guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:30.50,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Childhood friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:33.84,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you're so casual with each other's names.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:38.41,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you can call me by my name too, Nishimi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:43.61,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And then maybe I'll call you... "Kaoru-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:45.72,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaoru-san, Kaoru-san, Kaoru-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:48.27,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What is this echoing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:50.63,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I said that without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.33,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:53.98,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine! I don't mind it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:58.16,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right... Ri... chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:15:58.94,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:02.70,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you happen to know of a record shop in town that sells classical music?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.48,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Records?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.67,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,We've got tons of records at my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:08.00,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You should come over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:12.70,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I really mean by inviting you over...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:13.77,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:16.92,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I think things are moving too fast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:20.41,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this how Kyushu girls behave?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:24.53,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This is our shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:26.56,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And this is my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:27.64,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Fath...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:31.51,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,M-My name is Nishimi Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:33.68,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Your daughter has been very kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.60,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The classical records are over on that shelf, Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.30,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:44.69,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of records are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:46.76,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, piano music.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.30,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I play the piano myself, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:51.65,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You play the piano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:54.33,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's not a big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:55.11,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:57.95,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.87,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Outsiders aren't allowed in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:01.54,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:04.34,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san is a good friend of mine and Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:05.85,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sen's?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:09.20,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not his friend, just a...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:10.35,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:15.33,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:20.77,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.57,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doin' here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:41.61,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's what I want to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.06,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Rikko! We've got an intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.62,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to this, Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:48.10,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san says he can play piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:51.14,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:55.20,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But bet you anything it's just rich kid, stuffed shirt classical stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:58.51,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Jazz is the only music for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:36.30,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:38.04,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:41.59,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Kaoru-san, go on and play the piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:42.64,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.56,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Rikko,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.76,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,only jazz is allowed in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:51.08,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the piano you want, I'll play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:03.39,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, I know this piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:06.82,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear any more. It's like {\i1}this{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:15.42,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.16,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't even close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.17,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:19.64,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I played it exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:21.17,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't any {\i1}swing{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:24.59,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,If you play it without feelin', it ain't jazz to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:29.26,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I'd love to hear you two do a session together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:30.41,Default,Kaoru & Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:33.62,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, Rikko. That's a no-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:37.99,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This guy doesn't get jazz at all, and he's got no sense for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:41.12,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,A little practice, and playing that'll be a cinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:47.14,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:49.66,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.05,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Come back again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:58.61,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan, do you know the name of the tune he was playing on the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:00.97,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:04.51,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing Sen can play on the piano is the intro to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:09.36,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Art Blakey and the Jazz Messengers' "Moanin'."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.49,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like this, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:21.68,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he here to buy classical music?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:22.61,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:31.72,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know why...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:37.60,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but his drums just wouldn't stop thundering in my head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:41.67,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:43.91,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:46.36,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you walking strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:48.60,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Really? This is how I always walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:53.23,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:56.70,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Rikko! Bon! See ya'!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:05.45,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're running down this slope that I hate so much like it's nothing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:10.26,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What can you see beyond the hill?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:15.76,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it an outlook I've never seen before?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
